<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301993>
    dc:description "FIGURES 29–34. Male genitalia and female ovipositor of Dicranomyia (Erostrata) yazuensis sp. nov. 29: Male genitalia (holotype) in dorsal view; 30: Internal structure of male genitalia in dorsal view; 31: Paramere of male genitalia in outer view; 32: Female ovipositor (paratype) in lateral view; 33: Sternite 8 and hypogynial valve in ventral view; 34: Furca in ventral view. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1301993/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301995>
    dc:description "FIGURES 35–40. Adults of Dicranomyia (Erostrata) spp. 35: D. (E.) globithorax; 36: D. (E.) globulithorax; 37: D. (E.) submelas sp. nov.; 38: D. (E.) reniformis sp. nov.; 39: D. (E.) tabashii; 40: D. (E.) yazuensis sp. nov. Scale bars = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1301995/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301997>
    dc:description "FIGURES 41–44. Distributions of Japanese species of Dicranomyia (Erostrata). 41: D. (E.) globithorax (red circle) and D. (E.) globulithorax (blue triangle); 42: D. (E.) submelas sp. nov.; 43: D. (E.) reniformis sp. nov. (red circle) and D. (E.) yazuensis sp. nov. (blue triangle); 44: D. (E.) tabashii." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1301997/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

